<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/563986.The_South_vs_The_South"><img alt="The South vs. The South: How Anti-Confederate Southerners Shaped the Course of the Civil War" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348509688l/563986._SX98_.jpg" />
